000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcba6208944ca500fbe8c7a336be81fcf6c7c533","tid":1537112,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:17:22.000Z","msg":"所羅門要決定應該把孩子交給那一個婦人。他沉思了一會，叫人拿來一把刀，命令身邊的人說：「將孩子劈成兩半，一半給那婦人，一半給這婦人。」聽到這個裁決，其中一個婦人立刻哀求說：「大王，千萬不可把孩子劈開，請你把他交給另外那婦人吧，讓孩子活著！」另一個婦人卻說：「大王，這孩子不歸我，也不歸她，把他劈開吧！」所羅門聽了，立刻斥退這不顧孩子死活的狠婦，將嬰兒交給寧可讓出孩子也要讓他活著的婦人，因為愛護孩子的才是真媽媽。"},{"pid":"12135df150ababd3ad1e97a895121aa1793de26c","tid":1537112,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf62bdf4130b51c61c4f702b97de0643d5937e44","tid":1537112,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b3d41b957dffa5840756bceae9d86d6f4d7270b","tid":1537112,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:32:55.000Z","msg":"我記得個陣解決軍仲射爆咗國泰架客機<br />\n要挾英國還香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:35:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%9C%B8%E7%8E%8B%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E8%90%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%259C%25B8%25E7%258E%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=189ba6ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%9C%B8%E7%8E%8B%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E8%90%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a><br />\n真係意外定要挾無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:55:46.000Z","msg":"結果下一個星期咪比美國航空母艦報仇<br />\n擊落兩隻中共戰鬥機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ba6ca8ce34052a496e624d4364ac5721cd3fe6","tid":153711